snippet.title: Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek - Lyrical | The Devil | Darshan | Prakash Veer | B Ajaneesh Loknath
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe üëâ https://bit.ly/Saregama_Kannada

Presenting the Lyrical of ''Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek'' from the much-awaited film ''The Devil'' featuring Challenging Star Darshan. Shri Jaimatha Combines, in association with Saregama a Yoodlee Films, presents the much-awaited film The Devil. Tune in now and feel the vibe. 

Song Credits:
Song Name : Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek
Music Composed, Arranged & Programmed By : B Ajaneesh Loknath
Singer : Deepak Blue
Lyrics : Aniruddha Sastry
Choreographer : Santhu Master
Additional Vocals : B Ajaneesh Loknath, Aniruddha Sastry & Group
Keyboard : B Ajaneesh Loknath, V Sukumar
Rhythm : Ricky D‚ÄôCosta, Kalyan Chakravarthy, Sukumar V, B Ajaneesh Loknath
Mixed & Mastered By : Sanjay Kumar M P, Renu Digi Studio, Bangalore
Music Production : C R Bobby, B Ajaneesh Loknath, Abbs Studios Bangalore

Movie Credits:
Starring : Challenging Star Darshan, Rachana Rai, Mahesh Manjrekar, Achyuth Kumar, Sharmila Mandre.
Produced by: J Jayamma & Saregama
Directed by: Prakash Veer
Executive Producer : Thashwini Veer
Dialogue : Kanth Raj S S
Direction Department : Mohan Malagi, M S Abishaik, B. Thimme Gowdaa, Purnima Deshpande, Mallik R, Bharath, Chandrakumar, Yuvraj Hemanth, Sanjana Sudhakarr
Director Of Photography (DOP) : Sudhakarr S Raj
Music Director : B Ajaneesh Loknath, Abbs Studios
Editor : Harish Komme
Art Director : Mohan B Kere
Action Director : Ram Lakshman
Colourist : Ashwath
Post Production : Annapurna Studios
Managers : Suresh K Mysore, Jagadish Rao R.
Still Photography : Kadur Raghu & Kadur Yogi
Lyrical Video : Gowtham Raj (Single Frame Studio)
Poster Design : Ashwin Ramesh (Win Designs)
PRO : Sudhindra Venkatesh

Lyrics:
Rap:
Hey Gijigalakama Rakaa Lakama
Gijigalakama Rakaa
Lights On Andare Lit Aag Battaare
Blockbusterrr Pakka

Generation To Generationu
Mugi Beeltaar Egga Mugga
Aye Chinna Oy Chinna
He Breaks All Time Records

Pallavi:
Nammovrene Nange Bossu
Nanu Badkod For The Fansu
Khaasa Aadre Daasa Naanu
Dosti Nibhaaisu

First Day First Show Theatre Alli
Damaal Dimeel Soundinalli !!
Celebration Maadovr Nijvaad Celebritiesu

Hasividdare Saadhne Maadona
Kashta Padovrge Keerti Nidhaana
Namma Bhaashene Nange Pradhaana
Nera Nudile Helteen Kelanna

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek

Rap:
Hey Gijigalakama Rakaa Lakama
Gijigalakama Rakaa
Lights On Andare Lit Aag Battaare
Blockbusterrr Pakka

Generation To Generationu
Mugi Beeltaar Egga Mugga
Aye Chinna Oy Chinna
Forever Record Breaks

Charanam 1:
Cut-Out Andre Naan Antaare
Daulat Ella‚Ä¶ No Chance

Yaariginta Naaven Kammi
Anta Aagu‚Ä¶ Advance

Ille Hutti Ille Beledu Niyattaagi Ille Duddu
Oorudhdhaara Maadovr Naavu Pakka Localsu!

Yeshte Saahukaara Idru Oorigoore Kondkondidru
Nanna Preetsovr Maatra Nange Celebritiesu

Yene Aagogli
Cho-Ninna Bidovr Naavalla

Nanna Mansalli
Cho-Hachcheyaagirteev Naavella

Beda Namage Berevr Kathe Puraana
Nera Nudile Matte Helteen Kelanna

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek

|| Rap Repeat ||

Charanam 2:
Oyy
Cho-Yenappa
Actually En Gotta Chinna
Cho-Helappa

Ninna Belavanige Ninna Kaiyyalle
Make Your Future Brightu!
Hit Aagodmele Nam Hudga Annovrge
Don‚Äôt Need To Be Sweetu!

Prathibhege Illi Kone Illa..
KaleLyoru Kammi Illa‚Ä¶

Nuggi Neevu Munde Bandu Nintre‚Ä¶
Nimge Yashassu

Akkapakkadavra Maatu Keli..
Addressgildang Aagogbedi‚Ä¶
Nimma Nambirovrigella
Neeve Taane The Bossu!!

Nimma Preetige Chiraruni Naa
Ella Nammovre Anta Baalona

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek!!

|| Rap Repeat ||

Idre Nemdiyaag Irbek!!

snippet.title: Baahubali - The Epic Teaser | Prabhas, Rana Daggubati | SS Rajamouli | 31st October 2025
snippet.description:
Baahubali The Epic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW

Screenplay & Direction: S.S. Rajamouli
Presented by: K. Raghavendra Rao B.A.
Producers: Shobu Yarlagadda & Prasad Devineni
Story: V. Vijayendra Prasad 
DOP: K.K. Senthil Kumar
Production Designer: Sabu Cyril
Music Composer: M.M. Keeravaani
VFX Supervision: V. Srinivas Mohan
Sound Design: P.M. Satheesh
Stunt Choreography: Peter Hein
Additional Stunts: King Solomon, Lee Whittakar, Kaloyan Vodenicharov
Dance Choreographers: Prem Rakshit, Shankar, Dinesh Kumar, Jani
Editor: Tammiraju 
Costume Designer: Rama Rajamouli, Prashanti Tripirneni 
Dialogues:
Telugu - C.H. Vijay Kumar, Ajay Kumar G
Hindi - Manoj Muntashir
Tamil - Karky

snippet.title: Ufff Yeh Siyapaa Trailer | G.Ashok | A.R. Rahman | Sohum, Nushrratt, Nora, Omkar, Sharib | 5th Sept
snippet.description:
In this uniquely wordless comedy of errors, Kesari Lal Singh (Sohum Shah), a sheepish common man, finds himself entangled in a spiraling mess when his wife, Pushpa (Nushrratt Bharuccha), leaves him - convinced he‚Äôs been flirting with their neighbour, Kamini (Nora Fatehi). He hasn‚Äôt. But before he can clear his name, a wrongly delivered drug parcel sets off a chain of escalating disasters, the worst of which is a dead body turning up in his home. As Kesari scrambles to fix the situation, another corpse appears - turning his house into a full-blown crime scene. To make matters worse, Police Inspector Hasmukh (Omkar Kapoor) arrives with a personal agenda of his own, only adding to the madness. What follows is a wildly absurd, darkly comic chain of events - unfolding without a single spoken word.

Ufff Yeh Siyapaa releases in theatres on 5th September 2025.

Starring: Sohum Shah, Nushrratt Bharuccha, Nora Fatehi, Omkar Kapoor and Sharib Hashmi
Presented By: Luv Films
Written & Directed By: G. Ashok
Produced By: Luv Ranjan and Ankur Garg
Music By: A.R. Rahman

Also known as recut trailers, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies A New And Fresh Story, editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer teaser Glimpse are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film..
The trailer mashups are not only a user generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. snippet.title: Sumit Parta - Sabhi Khaas (Official Music Video) | New Haryanvi Song 2025 | Real Music
snippet.description:
Presenting ‚ÄúSabhi Khaas‚Äù ‚Äì the 2025 Haryanvi Hip Hop Anthem by Sumit Parta. 
Raw bars. Street energy. Real talk. 
This track hits hard with loyalty, betrayal & brotherhood stories straight from Haryana‚Äôs rap scene.

With powerful lyrics, heavy delivery, and authentic street-style flow, Sumit Parta turns real-life struggles into a bold hip hop statement. Sabhi Khaas is more than just a song ‚Äî it‚Äôs a reality check on friendship, fake loyalty, and survival.

Blending smooth Haryanvi lyrics with a pan-India rap appeal, this track connects with anyone who knows the grind. If you‚Äôre looking for authentic Haryanvi hip hop, Sabhi Khaas is your soundtrack.

Hard Bars. Real Emotions. Pure Haryana Vibes.
This is the voice of new-age Haryanvi rap and Indian hip hop.

snippet.title: LAZY BOY / SUNEP LEMTUR (NAGAMESE COMEDY SONG)
snippet.description:
‚ÄúLazy Boy‚Äù is a thought-provoking music video that portrays the life of a matured, overage, and unmarried man who has failed to find success in life. Despite trying every possible job opportunity, he never manages to pass an interview, leaving his parents deeply frustrated and disappointed with his choices. With no career, no ambition, and no direction, he spends his days idly alongside Bokali‚Äîanother unmarried woman of 49‚Äîwhose only interest lies in chasing much younger guys.

Through humor, irony, and a touch of raw honesty, the video highlights a section of reality in today‚Äôs society: individuals who, despite age and maturity, still struggle to find purpose and stability in life. ‚ÄúLazy Boy‚Äù is not just entertainment‚Äîit‚Äôs a mirror reflecting the struggles, flaws, and societal challenges many face in the modern world.
Enjoy Watching üôè

I want to sincerely thank my brother  & friend Mr. Teeya Imsong, for his dedication and sacrifice in bringing my song ‚ÄúLazy Boy‚Äù to life. Your skillful mixing and mastering gave the song its true identity and soul. I deeply appreciate your hard work, patience, and commitment in shaping this project into something special.
